data.description: This charming single story traditional has great curb appeal & tons of potential for bringing your HGTV design ideas to life! Smartly designed with functionality in mind, offering an expansive formal living & formal dining area with plenty of room for those large Holiday gatherings----while the open airy family room & kitchen creates the ideal space for easy entertaining & socializing while cooking! Oversized laundry room off the kitchen has lots of shelving & storage space perfect for those bulk grocery hauls and keeping organized! The primary retreat offers a large walk-in closet, and a private ensuite that features a walk-in shower & jetted tub to unwind after a long day! This fabulous outdoor area has a custom covered patio perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or summer parties & backyard BBQs with friends & family! Nature enthusiasts will love being in close proximity to a naturally preserved walking trails, great for morning jogs & evening strolls with the fur babies!
